{"title":"红小鬼","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":6,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红小鬼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一个叫你红小鬼？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从有了这活泼的名字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红军中便有了一支孩子的部队。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁？是谁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一个叫你红小鬼？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从有了这响亮的名字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共和国便有了一批年幼的先辈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁？是谁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一个叫你红小鬼？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从有了这悲壮的名字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你便永远挺立在十几岁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有的红领巾都是今天的红小鬼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有的红小鬼都是明天的丰碑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有的丰碑都刻写着你的故事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有的故事都在祖国的蓝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上放飞。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}